M&S Begins New Pay Structure Talks With Shareholders, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-01T00:39:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/m-s-begins-new-pay-structure-talks-with-shareholders-ft-says.html
Marks & Spencer Group Plc (MKS)  has begun
discussing with shareholders a new executive pay structure aimed
at linking pay awards more closely with Chief Executive Officer
 Marc Bolland ’s strategic plans, the Financial Times reported,
without attribution. The consultation talks on the new pay
proposals are “constructive,” the FT said, citing a major
shareholder.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 